terms.title: Excellence
terms.Text: The quality of being outstanding or extremely good:

terms.title: Mindsight
terms.Text: "Mindsight" is a term coined by Dr. Dan Siegel to describe our human capacity to perceive the mind of the self and others.

terms.title: Transformational Purpose Statement
terms.Text: A statement that articulates a coach's intent to transform the lives of his/her players.
